Ing '''Shàntóu''' ({{zh|c=汕头}}), a ausan da muring '''Swatow''' o '''Suátao''', metung yang [[lakanbalen a kadaneng prefecture]] (''prefecture-level city'') king [[aslagan]] nang bebe dayatmalat ning lalawigan ning [[Guangdong]], [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina]], a maki pangkabilugan a poplasyun a  5,391,028 anyang 2010 at maki lapad a administratibung {{convert|2,064|km2|sp=uk}}. Kayabe ya ampo reng lakanbalen ning [[Jieyang]] ampong  [[Chaozhou]], ing labuad a metropolitanu – a mayayaus [[Chaoshan]] – maki lapad yang {{convert|10,404|km2|abbr=on}}, at maki permanenti yang populasyun a 13,937,897 anyang wakas ning 2010.

